            <div class="faq-a">Yes &mdash; for private bank wealth managers at JPMorgan, Goldman, Morgan Stanley, UBS, BAML with W-2 + production bonus + AUM-fee participation + deferred compensation + RSU, see our <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/professional-services/">professional services hub</a> for multi-source variable income synthesis under Fannie Mae B3-3.1-01.</div>
